Body: Description: I'd like to request the latest client software packages for Linux. I'd like to get the latest version available for Ubuntu 22.04, Ubuntu 24.04, Fedora 40, and Fedora 41 respectively.

What We've Learned Updated: Customer would like to receive the latest EPP clients for the following OSs: 
Ubuntu 22 24 Fedora 40 41
Next Steps Updated: We have provided them all the links, so they can download the clients.
